high_descs: Turn left and take a step forward, then turn right and walk forward, turn right to face the small white end table next to the sink.
Pick up the rightmost blue spray bottle off of the end table.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn right and walk over to the wall, turn right again to face the toilet and look down.
Put the spray bottle in the grey bin that is next to the toilet.
Walk over to the small white end table on your right.
Pick up the blue spray bottle off of the end table.
Walk over to the small grey bin behind you.
Put the blue spray bottle in the small grey bin.
anns.task_desc: Move two spray bottles into a small grey bin.

high_descs: Walk over to the white drawers to the right of the sink.
Pick up the spray bottle on the right.
Turn around and face the bin that's next to the toilet.
Place the bottle down in the bin.
Walk back over to the white drawers.
Pick up the spray bottle from the white drawers.
Walk back over to the bin next to the toilet.
Put the spray bottle in the bin.
anns.task_desc: To move two spray bottles to the bin next to the toilet.

high_descs: Turn left for one step, turn right for three steps, and then turn right to face the table.
Pick up the blue spray bottle on the right of the table.
Turn right for one step, turn right and walk to the wall then turn right again.
Put the spray bottle in the trash can, nozzle facing left, on the side closest to you.
Turn right for one step, turn left for one step, and then turn right and walk straight to the table.
Pick up the blue spray bottle.
Turn right for one step, turn right and walk to the wall then turn right again.
Put the spray bottle in the trash can, next to the spray bottle already there but with the nozzle pointed north.
anns.task_desc: Put two blue spray bottles in the trash can.
